original_title: Paw Patrol: Pups Save the Kittens
overview: It's PAW Patrol to the rescue in this PURR-fect collection of 6 adventures featuring the Mischievous Kittens! Also, don't miss when the Pups pounce into action to create the best pizza ever, or when they have to rescue Skye after she crash lands on Jake's Mountain!
title: Paw Patrol: Pups Save the Kittens
